<item>
            <title>[FLINK-2321] The seed for the SVM classifier is currently static</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2321</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The seed for the SVM algorithm in FlinkML has a default value of 0, meaning that if it&apos;s not set, we always have the same seed when running the algorithm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What should happen instead is that if the seed is not set, it should be a random number.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
